subject: Golf
Kraft Nabisco Championship (Golf)
lead_paragraph: Inbee Park of South Korea birdied the first two holes on her way to a four-stroke victory over So Yeon Ryu in the Kraft Nabisco Championship, moving to No. 2 in the world rankings.
